data.description: Welcome to this perfectly located home placed in the highly sought-after Carl Albert High School district! This charming residence boasts a spacious floorplan including a cozy fireplace, and a well-appointed eat-in kitchen with a convenient breakfast bar that seamlessly opens to one of the two generously sized living spaces. The large primary suite offers two closets and a luxurious, jetted tub with an oversized shower featuring dual, rain-head shower heads. Updates include 2020 vinyl flooring, privacy fence, garage door motor, gutters and water heater. More recently the kitchen, dining, and primary bathroom have also been freshly painted. Outside you can find a true oasis, complete with a covered patio and pond. Located in close proximity to Tinker AFB, Downtown Oklahoma City, and SE 29th Shopping Center & Restaurants, this home offers an opportunity you don't want to miss!
